<title>
Rear Axle Inspection
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A2306007">Rear Axle Removal and Installation</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Inspect rear axle (1) for deformation and damage.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Inspect rear axle bushings (2) for crack, deformation and damage. If check result is not OK, replace rear axle assembly with new one.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
